### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@adminToken = your-admin-access-token

### Get all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### Get all categories (including inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories?includeInactive=true

### Get category tree
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/tree

### Get category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/303a86d9-b62a-427f-93cc-5f4b2a5d10f9

### Get category by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/slug/phone

